PrecisAppointment of Alexandra Bugailiskis as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Italian Republic and as Permanent Representative of Canada to the Food and Agriculture Organization, the World Food Programme and the International Fund for Agricultural Development, with concurrent accreditation as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Republic of San Marino, with residence in Rome; Lilian Chatterjee as High Commissioner for Canada in the Co operative Republic of Guyana and as Plenipotentiary Representative of Canada to the Caribbean Community (CARICOM); Jeff David as Consul General of Canada in Chongqing (People’s Republic of China); Jess Dutton as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Arab Republic of Egypt; Heidi Hulan as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Republic of Austria and as Ambassador and Permanent Representative to the International Organizations, with concurrent accreditation as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Slovak Republic, with residence in Vienna; Kyle Nunas as Consul General of Canada in Ho Chi Minh City (Socialist Republic of Vietnam); Benoit Préfontaine as High Commissioner for Canada in the People’s Republic of Bangladesh; and Nicolas Simard as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Democratic Republic of the Congo.
